<h3>Getting ccollect</h3>
<h4>via git</h4>
The project name of ccollect is "<i>cLinux/ccollect.git</i>".
<A HREF="http://unix.schottelius.org/git/">Read how to get a project via git.</A>
Alternatively, you can
<A HREF="http://unix.schottelius.org/cgi-bin/gitweb.cgi?p=cLinux/ccollect.git;a=summary">look
at the current status in git</A>
